Vendored copy of https://github.com/eliben/pycparser, with some patches to accept various C syntax extensions.

This is a copy of m2c's m2c_pycparser/ directory with the only difference being a renaming (to avoid conflicts
if both permuter and m2c are installed). Latest m2c commit: 567e39f59b963b73342c14000e2bd7aab7d3f719
